ore Services</h3>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-server\"></i>\n                    <h4>Cloud Solutions</h4>\n                    <p>Migrate and manage your operations in the cloud with our expert services.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-network-wired\"></i>\n                    <h4>Network Design</h4>\n                    <p>Build and optimize high-performance networks tailored to your needs.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    <h4>Cybersecurity</h4>\n                    <p>Protect your assets with cutting-edge security strategies and monitoring.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-database\"></i>\n                    <h4>Data Management</h4>\n                    <p>Ensure the integrity and accessibility of your critical data.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About Apex Infrastructure Solutions</h3>\n            <p>With years of experience, our team is dedicated to delivering exceptional IT infrastructure services. We partner with you to understand your unique challenges and provide solutions that are not only effective but also forward-thinking.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get in Touch</h3>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-phone\"></i>\n                    <h4>Call Us</h4>\n                    <p>+1 (123) 456-7890</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i>\n                    <h4>Email Us</h4>\n                    <p>info@apexinfra.com</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-map-marker-alt\"></i>\n                    <h4>Visit Us</h4>\n                    <p>123 Tech Avenue, Silicon Valley, CA 94000</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Infrastructure Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Building the future of IT, one solution at a time.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}